The Great Earl Havoton: Beloved Founder of Havoton
A visionary, trailblazer, and absolute icon.
This ambitious man, with an unhealthy obsession for
Halloween and the supernatural, first ventured to what is now
the Town of Havoton to investigate the rise in
supernatural sightings he had read in the papers.
According to local legends, what Earl discovered was groundbreaking,
enough to drive him to his ultimate demise. What exactly did he
find? Unfortunately Earl took that secret with him to his grave.
Nevertheless, his accomplishments have not gone unnoticed.
Thanks to Earl Havoton's great efforts and determination,
he was able to capitalize on the strange energy of the area,
eventually transforming the once empty field into the
beautiful town and bustling tourist attraction it is today.
